# Configuration & Security

- Load config with src.shared.config.environment.load_config(...).
- Never hardcode credentials; use env vars and environment YAML.
- Validate config; fail fast on missing/invalid keys.

Example:
```python
from src.shared.config.environment import load_config
result = load_config(env_override="development", config_file="ADEF/config/environments/development.yml")
```

